{
  "texts": [
    "These include QUADAS and QUADAS-2 for diagnostic accuracy studies, ROBIS for systematic reviews [11] and PROBAST [12] for prediction modelling studies.",
    "Moreover, there is shared learning from the development of AI-specific reporting guidelines and risk of bias tools, including STARD-AI [10] and PROBAST-AI [13].",
    "The development of QUADAS-AI can be distilled into broad three stages, as previously delineated [14].",
    "Given the pressing need for suitable quality assessment standards of diagnostic studies in this field, development is projected to finish by Q4 2024.",
    "Stage 1 Project organisation:QUADAS-AI is being undertaken by a Project Team and a Steering Committee."
  ]
}